{"tid":2428331,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"申請BNO簽證要留意！如以App去掃描特區護照個晶片，國籍會顯示CHN而無法繼續申請","createTime":"2021-03-01T12:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T18:46:29.000Z","uid":28114,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e72f7069dd2982eb6522275af067d6766a5c7521","tid":2428331,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:49:51.000Z","msg":"提提大家，如果以App去掃描特區護照個晶片，國籍會自動顯示為CHN。<br />\n<br />\n因為呢本嘢嘅簽發國去到國籍都係CHN，所以閣下要喺網站入去自行修改國籍做HKG，否則無法繼續申請BNO Visa。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️1997年主權移交後已經係HKG呢個國籍，特區護照係中國護照一種！<br />\n<br />\n#BNO #英國 #英國國民海外 #移民英國<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vitHrxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvitHrxv.jpg&h=564a72c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/490982747916524/posts/1545598099121645/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F490982747916524%2Fposts%2F1545598099121645%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt12sgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=0355ae61\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/490982747916524/posts/1545598099121645/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"d1e0fdca50b6696fec1023dff38015f2b1ffba54","tid":2428331,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6f9bc3ebf365b4f733b07a79239dc991144dbb","tid":2428331,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8b52d674f89666fde08c281d340feb37fc6befdb","tid":2428331,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:55:56.000Z","msg":"點解要用英國 APP SCAN 特區護照？"},{"pid":"f8257123b9c40c192de2b91ee57f4ef1d4b703fa","tid":2428331,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b52d674f8966